description: EUtraNetwork: Table containing E-UTRA network data, including timestamps, location, cell identifiers, and metadata.  dateTime: Timestamp of the data record; Area_Name: Name of the network area; CellId: Unique identifier for the cell site; Id2:  Redundant cell identifier; Id3:  Unknown identifier; vsDataType: Data type identifier; vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format; EUtraNetwork.userLabel: User-defined label (currently empty); EUtraNetwork.eUtraNetworkId: E-UTRA network ID.
